          "scid": "thig1.1:1.0.3",
          "en": "1. A Bhikkhunī of Name Unknown"
        },
        {
          "scid": "thig1.1:1.0.4",
          "en": "Namo tassa Bhagavato Arahato Sammāsambuddhassa."
        },
        {
          "scid": "thig1.1:1.0.5",
          "en": "“Sleep softly, little Sturdy, take thy rest At ease, wrapt in the robe thyself hast made. Stilled are the passions that would rage within, Withered as potherbs in the oven dried."
        },
        {
          "scid": "thig1.1:1.0.6",
          "en": "Verse uttered by a certain Sister, a Bhikkhunī of Name Unknown"
